            <iframe  src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3429.854737555212!2d76.76584651172745!3d30.722483874483224!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390fedad88991a07%3A0xb4de516e9171f70e!2sNetmax%20Technologies%20Private%20Limited!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1765522409799!5m2!1sen!2sin" height="450" style="border:0;width:100%;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
